15159 /******************************************************************************/
15160 /* For a painless codes migration between the STM32F7xx device product */
15161 /* lines, the aliases defined below are put in place to overcome the */
15162 /* differences in the interrupt handlers and IRQn definitions. */
15163 /* No need to update developed interrupt code when moving across */
15164 /* product lines within the same STM32F7 Family */
15165 /******************************************************************************/
15166 
15167 /* Aliases for __IRQn */
15168 #define HASH_RNG_IRQn RNG_IRQn
15169 
15170 /* Aliases for __IRQHandler */
15171 #define HASH_RNG_IRQHandler RNG_IRQHandler
